                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column">

                        <div class="row how_it_works">
                            <div class="col-md-12 mb-5 how_main_title">
                                <h3>
                                    How it works
                                </h3>
                                <p class="pt-5">
                                    Whether you are looking for your first job or looking for a change in career. GetaJobGH helps you find the right job easily 
                                </p>
                            </div>


                            <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
                                <div class="how_title">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span> Search Jobs </span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="how_desc pt-3">
                                    <p>
                                        We have jobs in the most popular industries and with top companies. 
                                        Plus, you can create alerts so you never miss a job opportunity.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
                                    <div class="how_title">
                                        <i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span> Create a Profile and Get Noticed </span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="how_desc pt-3">
                                        <p>
                                            Put your best foot forward by creating a professional profile that would get you that dream job. Get noticed by thousands of recruiters.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
                                        <div class="how_title">
                                            <i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span> Apply for jobs </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="how_desc pt-3">
                                            <p>
                                                Apply to jobs that fit your work experience qualification and skills. We guarantee your safe and easy experience.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section_four">

        <div class="fouth_section">
            <div class="site_container">

                <div class="category_title_text text-center">

                    <h3>
